    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dedicated team of Runic Dices Entertainment presents to you: Nanokings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Nanokings is a Roguelite RPG Hack’N’Hell game where you must fight for your and your tribe’s survival in the world of Mykrafjordur.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prepare to fight and die over and over again in the name of your people!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/bad5d1159fe6a17484b5fac5ba80ac0b.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/bad5d1159fe6a17484b5fac5ba80ac0b.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/bad5d1159fe6a17484b5fac5ba80ac0b.mp4?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/50a5b1d59e1ed166738c7d932abe52c8.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1440 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face mutated creatures, who act on their primal instincts to rip you apart. Fight through the swarm of these vicious beings that surround you, evade their attacks, and kill them before they kill you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/b98e13270212f1240942450cf0bd8a88.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/b98e13270212f1240942450cf0bd8a88.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/b98e13270212f1240942450cf0bd8a88.mp4?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/0211f2d8e4d46e2e40fb070009931f4e.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/0211f2d8e4d46e2e40fb070009931f4e.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/0211f2d8e4d46e2e40fb070009931f4e.mp4?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/f0b9874ed283434a6958fa40f5f5994b.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1440 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle against enemy Viking tribes who seek to destroy you and your people. Take them down, from the pawns they send to the chieftain who rules over them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/010d3688469adda15bccd19981a69050.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/010d3688469adda15bccd19981a69050.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/010d3688469adda15bccd19981a69050.mp4?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/bade5d0852b3f14004843df31ec629af.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1440 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The mixed genre of Reverse Bullet Hell and Hack’n’Slash gives you two different ways of playing Nanokings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go through the different locations of Mykrafjordur for a Reverse Bullet Hell experience and travel through caves, crypts, and portals for that Hack’n’Slash game style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/84e355982aba14df70eb312616647e9f.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/84e355982aba14df70eb312616647e9f.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/db610307a059a10109654437bd9012d5.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1440 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose new characters and random weapons that are available to you in each gameplay and after every unlock. Collect new weapons, items, and attachments by completing quests, slaying your enemies, and destroying totems.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each time you enter a Stage it is different, with new paths and new obstacles to overcome, and always dangerous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/551769ac4214399c8a41bf3367a6c977.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1170 height=662 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/551769ac4214399c8a41bf3367a6c977.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/551769ac4214399c8a41bf3367a6c977.mp4?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/8756aa989363263883362773a0e3bb50.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1440 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After every run, you unlock parts of your skill tree and power-ups. Great combinations lead to stronger builds that push through to your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock more playable Vikings through the Brotherhood System, completing quests and convincing them to join your tribe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/31f294291b9da24f70c4c526b7b5449f.poster.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/31f294291b9da24f70c4c526b7b5449f.webm?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/31f294291b9da24f70c4c526b7b5449f.mp4?t=1771669882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142550/extras/014b793e9007353442604ee9c29eee58.avif?t=1771669882\" width=1444 height=168 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long after the destruction of humanity, a new era begins. The Earth as we know it had died and has been reborn into a new era, as Várenheim.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For centuries, animals have been evolving into monster-like creatures, with the hunger for blood and primal revenge against the humans responsible for their ancestral mutations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rise of humanoids had developed into tribes. They have discovered old Nordic artefacts and revived the stories of Norse Mythology. But with the entire world against them, it has become necessary to augment themselves with metallic arms, legs, or anything that may help them survive and endure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You play as the Vikings of Runik Dagaz, born into Mykrafjordur with a single purpose as the chosen. You are Vikings who are capable of reviving after death, and so you are the only ones who can protect your people from monsters and Vikings alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is your duty to survive with your fellow Viking tribe from the darkness of Mykrafjordur.</p>",
